OL,3,CHow has the Iran war impacted UK
OL,4,Cmortgages?
OL,6,FAs the Bank of England held interest
OL,7,Frates on Thursday, ITV News Economics
OL,8,FEditor Joel Hills explained why and to
OL,9,Fwhat extent the war in the Middle East
OL,10,Fis hitting the British economy
OL,12,FWith the war in Iran entering its
OL,13,Ffourth week, shockwaves have been sent
OL,14,Fthrough the global economy as oil
OL,15,Fprices have surged.
OL,17,FThe conflict's impact goes way beyond
OL,18,Ffuel and energy costs, with turmoil in
OL,19,Ffinancial markets also affecting
OL,20,Fpeople's pensions and mortgage rates.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
