OL,3,CHow has the Iran war impacted UK
OL,4,Cmortgages?
OL,6,FEarlier this week the Bank of England
OL,7,Fannounced it was holding the interest
OL,8,Frates at 3.75% earlier this week,
OL,9,Frather than cutting them, as it
OL,10,Fattempted to work towards its target
OL,11,Fof bringing inflation to its 2% target.
OL,13,FThe fallout in the mortgage market has
OL,14,Fnot been "quite as dramatic" as after
OL,15,Fthe mini-Budget of Liz Truss'
OL,16,Fgovernment in 2022, or during the
OL,17,FCovid pandemic, according to financial
OL,18,Finformation company Moneyfacts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
