OL,3,CHow has the Iran war impacted UK
OL,4,Cmortgages?
OL,6,FIn part, it says this because "the
OL,7,Fmortgage market was in pretty rude
OL,8,Fhealth with a record number of
OL,9,Favailable products going into this
OL,10,Flatest crisis", it adds.
OL,12,FHere is a snapshot of the mortgage
OL,13,Fmarket as of Saturday, March 21,
OL,14,Faccording to Moneyfacts:
