OL,3,CHow has the Iran war impacted UK
OL,4,Cmortgages?
OL,6,FAround a fifth of available mortgage
OL,7,Fproducts have been pulled and rates
OL,8,Fhave continued to climb at pace this
OL,9,Fweek as lenders scramble to keep up
OL,10,Fwith volatile swap rates," said Adam
OL,11,FFrench, head of consumer finance at
OL,12,FMoneyfacts.
OL,14,F"The combination of rising rates and
OL,15,Ffalling choice is a direct response to
OL,16,Fthe conflict in the Middle East which
OL,17,Fhas dramatically shifted expectations
OL,18,Faround inflation and interest rates.
