PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774224184
OL,3,CHow has the Iran war impacted UK
OL,4,Cmortgages?
OL,6,F"While a quicker resolution to the
OL,7,Fconflict could ease some of pressure
OL,8,Fon rates, the reality is that a more
OL,9,Fvolatile world is a more expensive
OL,10,Fworld.
OL,12,F"Even though the most competitive
OL,13,Fdeals will remain below average,
OL,14,Fanyone looking to buy or remortgage
OL,15,Fthis year needs to prepare for higher
OL,16,Fcosts than previously expected."
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
